data.description: Nestled in the heart of Creekside at Lorson Ranch, this charming 2021-built home is a gem waiting to be discovered. With its prime location, it's a stone's throw away from Peterson and Schriever Space Force Base and Fort Carson, making it a perfect haven for those who cherish the convenience of being close to everything. As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere that says, "Welcome home!" Boasting four cozy bedrooms and three modern bathrooms, offering ample space for family, guests, or a home office. The heart of the home, the kitchen is equipped with state-of-the-art appliances and plenty of counter space to whip up your favorite dishes. But the magic doesn't stop there. Venture outside to the newly added rear deck with gazebo and you'll find yourself in a private oasis. With no neighbors behind, your view extends to a serene trail and a picturesque pond, offering a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life. It's the perfect spot for morning coffees, evening BBQs, or simply soaking up the beauty of nature. Living in this neighborhood means more than just owning a house; it's about being part of a vibrant community. With numerous community events throughout the year, there's always an opportunity to connect, celebrate, and create lasting memories with neighbors and friends. This home isn't just a place to live; it's a gateway to a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and community. Don't miss your chance to make it yours and start creating your own stories within its walls.
